<!-- What Is a 3-in-1 Wireless Charging Station -->
<section class="sec bg-white relative py-16">
 <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
 <h2 class="section-title text-center">What Is a 3-in-1 Wireless Charging Station?</h2>
 <p class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">A 3-in-1 wireless charging station simultaneously powers three devices — phone, smartwatch, and earbuds — from a single desktop dock. Built around the Qi2 MPP (Magnetic Power Profile) standard with N52H neodymium magnets, modern 3-in-1 stations deliver 15W-25W fast charging with perfect magnetic alignment. For B2B buyers, the 3-in-1 category commands the <strong>highest ASP in wireless charging</strong> ($50-150 retail), accounting for 18-25% of unit volume but 40-50% of category revenue.</p>

 <blockquote class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 bg-brandOrange/5 border-l-4 border-brandOrange rounded-r-xl px-6 py-5 text-sm text-slate-700 italic leading-relaxed">
  <p>"The global wireless charger market was valued at $6.78 billion in 2025 and is projected to reach $19.03 billion by 2030, growing at a 22.9% CAGR. Within this market, multi-device charging stations represent the highest-value segment — 60% of iPhone users also own an Apple Watch, 33% own AirPods, and 12% own all three devices. This 'Triple Threat' user base of approximately 170 million people represents the core addressable market for 3-in-1 charging stations."</p>
  <cite class="block text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2 not-italic">— <a href="https://www.grandviewresearch.com/industry-analysis/wireless-charger-market-report" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">Grand View Research</a>, Wireless Charger Market Report 2025-2030; <a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/09/18/apple-watch-airpods-play-a-bigger-role-in-apples-ecosystem-than-you-think" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">CIRP / AppleInsider</a>, Apple Ecosystem Ownership Data 2024</cite>
 </blockquote>

